{
  "stem": "1020.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But those years, they didn't have any telephones like we have in here to pick up a telephone and call somebody.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were lucky one way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we still couldn't trust with whom we're dealing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But some of them cooperated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were afraid for their lives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were afraid of the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Ukrainians, and the Lithuanians, and the Latvians, and the Polish-- they were our enemies-- the biggest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why Hitler built all those crematoriums on the Polish territory, That they were the biggest help.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you read now in the newspaper, every day you see somebody else is denaturalized from this country, taken away the citizenship.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you read the name, it's a Polack, or a Ukrainian, or a Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're not finding a German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you find all the other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were the help to destroy us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed in the forest until close to the end of '43, when the Russians start to get the upper hand in the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then when they took over territory, they reached where we were probably about three times on the Russian hands and on the German hands.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't want to get out from the underground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were unsure what-- in whose hands we'll fall in yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't want to fall back in the Russian hands, because I escaped from Siberia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was like in the middle of nowhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to only live with luck, with Gold's help, to drive, and survive, and fight through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, it was a big difference.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had three survivors-- three kind of survivors in this war-- people who went to concentration camp, destiny was dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By luck, they survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People were hidden on Aryan papers, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
